<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA4">
<l>āḷāṉō malla laṟiya muṟaiyiṭṭāṟ</l>
<l>kēḷāta teṉkolō kēḷāmai - nīḷākañ</l>
<l>cemmaiyā ṉākit tirumiṭaṟu maṟṟoṉṟā</l>
<l>memmaiyāṭ koṇṭa viṟai</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If [we] complain so that he would know the unhappiness of us who have become [his] servants,</l>
<l>will he not listen? There is no listening</l>
<l>in the lord who has taken us as servants,</l>
<l>in whom, while he is superb in [his] long body, the holy throat is something different.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
